'''''Tondar''''' was an [[CR92a Assassin-class corvette|''Assassin''-class corvette]] used by the [[Airam (group)|Airam]]. It was part of the joint-operation that was [[Mission to Kuras Drift|attacked]] by rival Airam clan leader [[Ilay]] and the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Wasp (Imperial-class)|''Wasp'']]. Fortunately the operation was a success and ''Tondar'' escaped into [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]].

